citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:05a on
15-Sep-16.
ACI Bartels knocked and rang the doorbell of the newer built house, knocked on the door of the older house, called
the main number provided and left a message, and called the cell phone number provided, but it was no longer
associated with the licensee.
